.SH NAME
CSSPerspective \- CSSPerspective
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]CSSPerspective\f[B]\f[R] interface of the CSS Typed
Object Model API represents the \f[CR]perspective()\f[R] value of the
individual \f[CR]transform\f[R] property in CSS.
It inherits properties and methods from its parent
\f[CR]CSSTransformValue\f[R].
.SH CONSTRUCTOR
.TP
\f[B]CSSPerspective()\f[R]
Creates a new \f[CR]CSSPerspective\f[R] object.
.SH INSTANCE PROPERTIES
.TP
\f[B]length\f[R]
Returns or sets the distance from z=0.
